				<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/304e7d66d22448703187ed510aba880a?s=40&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/304e7d66d22448703187ed510aba880a?s=80&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' />				<cite class="fn"><a href='http://kryptonradio.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Gene Turnbow</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>			</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->
				
